Description: Three views of Egypt in overlap; at top, river landscape with boats and buildings; below at left an arab man holding a pole or lance and another seated at a fire in front of a tent; at right, river landscape with boats and rocky plateau; proof illustration to 'The Illustrated London News'; after Georges Montbard. Wood-engraving
Producer name: Print made by: William Michael Roberts Quick
Acquisition name: Donated by: William Michael Roberts Quick
